nodes.text: Boboqueequee was a location in Hutt mythology, probably associated with the underworld. A common Huttese imprecation was "Rot in Boboqueequee!"
"Rot in Boboqueequee!" is one of several intentionally abstruse Huttese imprecations featured in the Jabba the Hutt series and is obviously the Huttese equivalent of "Burn in Hell!"
